message: /* Controversy */ Inside Paradeplatz is not well-regarded due to its poor reputation in Switzerland. While larger media houses may maintain credibility despite frequent exposure, smaller outlets like Inside Paradeplatz might not share the same level of seriousness. I propose removing this section and seeking input from an administrator to assess the appropriateness of such significant allegations based on a single, less reliable source.
/* Inside Paradeplatz as a reliable source? */ new section

/* Controversy */ This doesn't come from two separate sources; it's just one source. While both Insideparadeplatz and Blick.ch are mentioned, there's no relevant information about debts or related matters in Blick.ch, only in InsideParadeplatz. It's worth noting that Inside Paradeplatz is often subject to legal action and is not considered a highly reputable source. Given this lack of corroboration and reliability, it's important to exercise caution when considering this information.
